ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent patients transferred from an outpatient facility.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Encounter or attribute related to Admission Source. The intent of this data element is to identify environment types that define a transfer from an outpatient facility. ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with SNOMED CT codes to indicate outpatient facility environments.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
